column5: Just a quick note to all that I made it out today to my favorite trout spot with a perfect morning, water, and wind conditions. Notta a'gosh darn thing Oh well seeing as how I have not thrown a line for a bow in 5 years it was just nice to get out. I did however see a nice hen plucked out so they are comin!!! By next weekend things are gonna heat up and I will have pics  !!!! Oh god I am addicted again!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
